Company Overview of Coolfire Solutions, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Coolfire Solutions, Inc. develops situational awareness technology. The company offers Ronin, a mobile-first situational awareness platform that connects people, assets, and information in a way that leads to quick decision making and action taking. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in St. Louis, Missouri. Coolfire Solutions, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Coolfire Media Originals, LLC.


